    <title>Markdown 语法入门</title>
    <link href="http://www.chenzhenyuan.com/article/Markdown%20%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/"/>
    <id>http://www.chenzhenyuan.com/article/Markdown 语法入门/</id>
    <published>2017-07-08T06:26:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-07-08T06:26:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<a id="more"></a><p><ol class="toc toc-theme-wiki"><li class="toc-item level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#_4">标准标记</a></li><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#_5">标题</a></li><li class="toc-item level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#_Blockquotes_19">区块引用 Blockquotes</a></li><li class="toc-item level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#_29">绘制表格</a></li><li class="toc-item level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#_43">列表</a></li><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#_45">无序列表</a></li><li class="toc-item level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#_49">有序列表</a></li></ol><li class="toc-item level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#_51">高亮一段代码</a></li></ol><li class="toc-item level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#_54">扩展标记</a></li><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#_55">脚注</a></li><li class="toc-item level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#_62">制作一份待办事宜</a></li></ol></ol></p><h1><a id="_4"></a>标准标记</h1><h2><a id="_5"></a>标题</h2><p>Markdown 支持两种标题的语法，类 <a href="http://docutils.sourceforge.net/mirror/setext.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Setext</a> 和类 <a href="http://www.aaronsw.com/2002/atx/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">atx</a> 形式。</p><p>类 Setext 形式是用底线的形式，利用 = （最高阶标题）和 - （第二阶标题），例如：</p><pre><code>This is an H1=============This is an H2-------------</code></pre><h2><a id="_Blockquotes_19"></a>区块引用 Blockquotes</h2><p>Markdown 标记区块引用是使用类似 email 中用 &gt; 的引用方式。如果你还熟悉在 email 信件中的引言部分，你就知道怎么在 Markdown 文件中建立一个区块引用，那会看起来像是你自己先断好行，然后在每行的最前面加上 &gt; ：</p><blockquote><p>This is a blockquote with two paragraphs. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet,<br>consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aliquam hendrerit mi posuere lectus.<br>Vestibulum enim wisi, viverra nec, fringilla in, laoreet vitae, risus.</p><p>Donec sit amet nisl. Aliquam semper ipsum sit amet velit. Suspendisse<br>id sem consectetuer libero luctus adipiscing.</p></blockquote><h2><a id="_29"></a>绘制表格</h2><p>使用方式：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| PRODUCT    | PRICE   |  COUNT  |</span><br><span class="line">| --------   | ------: | :------:|</span><br><span class="line">| machine    |    1600 |    5    |</span><br><span class="line">| phone      |      12 |   12    |</span><br><span class="line">| other      |       1 |   234   |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编译结果：</p><table><thead><tr><th>PRODUCT</th><th style="text-align:right">PRICE</th><th style="text-align:center">COUNT</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>machine</td><td style="text-align:right">1600</td><td style="text-align:center">5</td></tr><tr><td>phone</td><td style="text-align:right">12</td><td style="text-align:center">12</td></tr><tr><td>other</td><td style="text-align:right">1</td><td style="text-align:center">234</td></tr></tbody><tbody></tbody></table><h2><a id="_43"></a>列表</h2><p>Markdown 支持有序列表和无序列表。</p><h3><a id="_45"></a>无序列表</h3><p>无序列表使用星号、加号或是减号作为列表标记：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*   Red</span><br><span class="line">*   Green</span><br><span class="line">*   Blue</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3><a id="_49"></a>有序列表</h3><h2><a id="_51"></a>高亮一段代码</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@requires_authorization</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">SomeClass</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pass</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">'__main__'</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># A comment</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">'hello world'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1><a id="_54"></a>扩展标记</h1><h2><a id="_55"></a>脚注</h2><p>使用方法：</p><p>$$E=mc^2$$</p><h2><a id="_62"></a>制作一份待办事宜</h2><ul><li><input type="checkbox" id="checkbox0"><label for="checkbox0">支持以 PDF 格式导出文稿</label></li><li><input type="checkbox" id="checkbox1"><label for="checkbox1">改进 Cmd 渲染算法，使用局部渲染技术提高渲染效率</label></li><li><input type="checkbox" id="checkbox2" checked="true"><label for="checkbox2">新增 Todo 列表功能</label></li><li><input type="checkbox" id="checkbox3" checked="true"><label for="checkbox3">修复 LaTex 公式渲染问题</label></li><li><input type="checkbox" id="checkbox4" checked="true"><label for="checkbox4">新增 LaTex 公式编号功能</label></li></ul><p><mark>marked</mark></p><p>29<sup>th</sup> | H<sub>2</sub>0<br><ins>inserted</ins></p><dl><dt>Term 1</dt><dd>asdf</dd><dd>fasd<br>with lazy continuation.<br>Second paragraph of the definition.</dd></dl><p><em>最新的webpack版本是：</em> <img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/v/webpack.svg?label=webpack&amp;style=flat-square&amp;maxAge=3600" alt="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;"></p><p>Double + single quotes replacement pairs, when typographer enabled,<br>and smartquotes on. Could be either a String or an Array.</p><p>JSON:</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"aa"</span>: <span class="string">"ass"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"sss"</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Javascript:</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> a = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> b = <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">V</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title">React</span>.<span class="title">Component</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    state = &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">constructor</span>() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">super</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    handleClick = <span class="function">(<span class="params">&#123;a, b&#125;</span>)=&gt;</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">const</span> &#123;a, b&#125; = <span class="keyword">this</span>.props;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    componentWillUpdate() &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    render() &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">Func</span>(<span class="params">a, b, v</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> Func(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">4</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>The <abbr title="Hyper Text Markup Language">HTML</abbr> specification<br>is maintained by the <abbr title="World Wide Web Consortium">W3C</abbr>.</p><p><sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn1" id="fnref1">[1]</a></sup>;</p><!-- 密码： 683541 --><hr class="footnotes-sep"><section class="footnotes"><ol class="footnotes-list"><li id="fn1" class="footnote-item"><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NodeJS 官网</a> <a href="#fnref1" class="footnote-backref">↩</a></p></li></ol></section>]]></content>
    
